quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  3,81,"“Ndipo (kumbukirani) pamene Allah adatenga lonjezo kwa aneneri, (n’kuwauza): “Ndikakupatsani buku ndi nzeru, nakudzerani Mtumiki wotsimikizira zomwe zili pamodzi ndi inu, mudzamkhulupirire ndi kumthangata.” (Allah) adatinso: “Kodi mwavomereza ndi kulandira pa zimenezi pangano langali?” (Iwo) adati: “Tavomereza.” (Iye) adati: “Tsono chitirani umboni, ine ndili pamodzi nanu mwa oikira umboni.”"
  3,82,"“Ndipo amene adzatembenuke pambuyo pa lonjezoli, (Allah adzawalanga chifukwa chakuti) iwo ngopandukiradi chilamulo cha Allah"
  3,83,"“Kodi akufuna chipembedzo chomwe si cha Allah pomwe chinthu chilichonse chili kumwamba ndi pansi chikugonjera Iye, mofuna kapena mosafuna? Ndipo onse adzabwezedwa kwa Iye"
  3,84,"“Nena: “Takhulupirira Allah ndi zomwe zavumbulutsidwa pa ife, ndi zomwe zidavumbulutsidwa kwa Ibrahim, ndi Ismail, Ishâq ndi Yaqub ndi zidzukulu (zake), ndi zimene adapatsidwa Mûsa ndi Isa (Yesu), ndi aneneri (ena) zochokera kwa Mbuye wawo. Sitisiyanitsa aliyense pakati pawo, ndipo ife kwa Iye ndi Asilamu (odzipereka kwathunthu).”"
  3,85,"“Ndipo amene angafune chipembedzo chosakhala Chisilamu, sichidzalandiridwa kwa iye. Ndipo iye tsiku lachimaliziro adzakhala mmodzi mwa (anthu) otaika"
  3,86,"“Kodi Allah angawaongole bwanji anthu omwe atuluka m’chikhulupiliro pambuyo pakukhulupirira natsimikiza kuti Mtumiki (uyu Muhammad{s.a.w}) ngoona, nkuwafikiranso zisonyezo zoonekera? Koma Allah saongola anthu ochita zoipa"
  3,87,"“Ndithu mphoto yawo ndiyakuti pa iwo pali matembelero a Allah, a angelo ndi anthu onse"
  3,88,"“M’menemo adzakhala nthawi yaitali; ndipo sichidzapeputsidwa chilango kwa iwo, ndiponso sadzapatsidwa danga"
  3,89,"“Kupatula anthu amene alapa, pambuyo pa zimenezo nachita zabwino. ndithudi, Allah Ngokhululuka, Ngwachisoni chosatha"
  3,90,"“Ndithudi, amene atuluka m’chikhulupiliro pambuyo pokhulupirira, kenako naonjezera kusakhulupirira, kulapa kwawo sikudzavomerezedwa konse. Ndipo iwo ndiosekera"
  3,91,"“Ndithudi amene sadakhulupirire, nkumwalira pamene ali osakhulupirira, sikudzalandiridwa kwa aliyense wa iwo ngakhale atapereka dipo la golide lodzadza dziko lonse. Iwo ndi omwe adzalandire chilango chopweteka, ndipo sadzakhala ndi athandizi"